      <description>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m Harsha. I&amp;rsquo;m a final year Dual Degree student in 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.cse.iitm.ac.in&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Department of Computer Science and Engineering&lt;/a&gt;
 at 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.iitm.ac.in&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Indian Institute of Technology Madras&lt;/a&gt;
. I am affiliated to RISE lab and 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://rbc-dsai.iitm.ac.in/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Robert Bosch Centre for Data Science and AI&lt;/a&gt;
. I am fortunate to have worked with 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.cse.iitm.ac.in/~ravi/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Prof. Balaraman Ravindran&lt;/a&gt;
 (my current Masters advisor) and 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.cse.iitm.ac.in/~sutanuc/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Prof. Sutanu Chakraborti&lt;/a&gt;
.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My research interests revolves around the fields of Deep Reinforcement Learning and Natural Language Processing and I am currently looking for PhD oppotunities relevant to my interests.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
